    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "makes sense. one more thing—when we're talking about cargo being lost or \"disappearing\" mid-transit, is it usually just accidents like storms, or are we actually looking at things like theft or piracy as a major risk factor for these routes? how do the Incoterms handle those kinds of unexpected \"disappearances\"?",
      "source": "evaluator"
